---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nuestro Espacio - URBANLIFT">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative h-[614px] flex items-end px-8 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 desaturate-[15%]" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD9zEMBwOmYsDANHlL-4XPSZMIgn_-dL3zxtjWQA4Z3m9McDHMu9-5e1tGwWRQHqTeJCCPle6QMOLlhBGDP9GG_I13uemMwU1MhdV_Dx9BSu2PvE1gopwhqBhjHNh7tbcTtQD9yy2DQT6DnedosQ1nDSD6U7pcoL2hDaUttZyAvxy2IMxLmia-ee7uToSI58NWc3wIO3bVZvMA9y3zc8EOj2ZyJ6B1baViIk3EFuQylThN3j7sL24Yayt9pkle9739JkiOMGUDjM5U" alt="Gym interior" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="font-headline text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.85] text-on-background">
          NUESTRO <br/> <span class="text-primary italic">SANTUARIO</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl font-light">
          Conoce nuestras instalaciones pensadas y diseñadas para ti. Entrena con el equipo de más alta calidad
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Bento Grid Zones Section -->
    <section class="px-8 py-24 bg-surface-container-lowest">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Zone: Calistenia -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none border-none bg-surface-container-high aspect-[3/4] md:aspect-auto">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBq8o3qx493MVZmUoNliaMYYcjdgMXDhNGgBkqqQjGCclardSNfnGYEabLoIRMPrqeApkIuF00p-l8N9Q1p7Bdb8IKLyHRFLU9WMEecjG5sU2h8j_o48fbdFC48VVttc1rLJQ1rV-B_l8KCiuiS0G4IDoArABbNB-JChlJ1qHojLCURq5dLpI2Y98QFNYu7GlHESMfTLtIi_rUgF39KDbhAw_hVWDusPynAZJrs0d9sQO_TbqMuIy17h8WlH9qWHpdxLB8sHP-QHZI" alt="Calistenia Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona calistenia y stret lifting</h3>
            <div class="h-1 w-0 group-hover:w-full bg-primary transition-all duration-500 mt-2"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Zone: Powerlifting -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none bg-surface-container-high aspect-video md:aspect-auto h-[300px]">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAklvuafn7V9iIy1ZypK08ZSgEUqNk4Cu2i23RShgBmcpfhY9S2uJsxRiLQzIDyEuKZxtVo599Z9e_ENwte3FwJ7ctjulN-fJYO7ZlFlPuBYAWH4IatpTImPuyHyIE5Pf8AkeEOUurvv913kXbAE66m5nZzvwL442rxE3MvCRDwgBzUkcXVBtYau_jj0Sv5js6BY8SEv_wUPWpRwB94uAxZ7CA3KDOePeZpursWxplLarDsEQEeTDECYJG3JDzTvKB16up3r0KB2t0" alt="Powerlifting Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona powerlifting</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Zone: Máquinas -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none bg-surface-container-high aspect-square">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCguMQFlOT1OKDLdA3m4v0mqZdXzuaYF4MKPSEa4K_E7bHOHz-xQP5ZZQOTn0DMPpdwWcMcuhKLU8881qVN7XY1lb-ONWrb7BnGp9j55i8G5PfTflJHuRMCnnmSTzkLgLWLZvXrkrqoJhHr03EuLc6dxylfZVmyT3y_aYXIaJnWMGPe8N02_I2WfseyLL5luKXQ7Epk2kUIcQg7dkOsVzDw2uUerLo3tCSwqzo6Ni7lqL8gU4cyBcpgvLLk353eA2aavLE-27OCrIY" alt="Machines Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona máquinas</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Zone: Peso Libre -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none bg-surface-container-high aspect-square">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDBhuxfQPl6j6YozwBUNwi38372m3eJFc7j6ek_T6Ya5Te5jB1bpmnse49n6EY4EiCRBKrBYv7TC2-6RwvNxUyArZzClZbuXS0IH3jI6lubleyUChlHy9DhUWCOLIaMTjwHyU-aeIIp7BRHpffX3f7vq7PRUtPqiJzT7ZfaAuh-Net7lVxAmej0QArCiLQ1RTxA-mswlp3zZnopBaZj0OwNBf99hZPexTtTpOvLlhKW5qs8Tqo0yuU0RYPhnDjumtazPujkQCHmm-0" alt="Free Weights Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona peso libre</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Zone: Descanso -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none bg-surface-container-high h-[400px]">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD20d6CH5U7lYloYovns5hQe5RUfFyYuQ2dIbjwlGCjT41BYWqyoVNitGw1V8J5t_KI2fo81vJMEEv-c2Gk7oj6cD4E7eVO1wMY_XiUT7ffD2hk9n6INLcxOZhLq_g_--EsXyqJMI6GP-IfH84aei_Mlu9SbRycPdZPGxDSjgygDer2Udi1vprCtBZ2gJOdpvDTI7Mj9SA1oQoFRzP7P7Bl1e1JLv-AeEIoQz4nOoeYKdPLh9SpgWcg0gK_NCTkd1qEH1BrdqyAzfs" alt="Lounge Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona de descanso</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Zone: Camarines -->
        <div class="md:col-span-5 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none bg-surface-container-high h-[400px]">
          <img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBl1sknUuS9_g6FqlYKkj62yQSiZXEc9Hy_vv8oigA__IgAHz_uwM9WPS0PlXH15T37Lw_Lk_F0bkLX40s3kbKeVsPZg1v4baIfFVO7WGX7kp48zZvbcHEO-_quDW82bnJH_juAk5FuduqyHbSbxfB9tJl2sgp_oK7BIldfy7BZ6lfCdvv3vHzPkQZ6AlY4IGRYQ5u4C2Q6aUyAgvCwqlCCnHxTKeKhy00xWD2AADy_belFhk2uXoYI1r89mCFhO9iJ2los4aZhLG8" alt="Locker Room Zone" />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8">
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Zona baños y camarines</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Trial Day Section -->
    <section class="px-8 py-24 bg-surface">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-none p-1 w-full relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
            <span class="font-headline text-9xl font-black text-primary select-none">$0</span>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-outline/20 p-8 md:p-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-primary-container/20 border border-primary/30 rounded-full">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
                <span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Pase Limitado</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">
                PRUEBA UN DÍA <br />
                <span class="text-primary">SIN COMPROMISO</span>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg font-light max-w-md">
                ¿Aún no te decides? Ven a conocer nuestra energía y equipamiento de primer nivel. Tu primer día corre por nuestra cuenta.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2">
                <span class="font-headline text-5xl font-bold text-primary">0$</span>
                <span class="text-on-surface-variant uppercase text-sm tracking-widest font-bold">Día Gratuito</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-[400px] bg-surface-container-high p-8 border border-outline-variant/30">
              <form class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-xs font-headline uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">Nombre Completo</label>
                  <input class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/30 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface/20 py-3 px-4 transition-all" placeholder="Ej. Juan Pérez" type="text" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-xs font-headline uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant mb-2">WhatsApp</label>
                  <input class="w-full bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/30 focus:border-primary focus:ring-0 text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface/20 py-3 px-4 transition-all" placeholder="+56 9 1234 5678" type="tel" />
                </div>
                <button class="w-full kinetic-gradient py-4 text-on-primary font-headline font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:brightness-110 transition-all mt-4" type="submit">
                  RESERVAR MI PASE GRATIS
                </button>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant/40 text-center uppercase tracking-tight">Válido solo para nuevos integrantes. Se requiere ID vigente.</p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
